Matthew D. Ellis -- Executive Vice President and Chief Financial Officer

We'll have to wait and see how the market develops over the fourth quarter. I'll tell you what, I'm very excited. When you think about having the best network both 4G and build in the best 5G network, you add it with the best device portfolio, you add that in with the best value proposition with what you've done with -- what we've done with Mix & Match 3.0, that is an incredible combination.

And so there is a number of levers available to us. But I'll tell you what, Brett, I'm very happy sitting here today, holding the card in my hand that we have and look forward to how the marketplace will develop in the fourth quarter.

