Kannan Venkateshwar -- Barclays -- Analyst

Thank you. So a couple if I could. I mean first is, Hans I mean on TracFone, could you just contextualize the objective why the change of heart in prepaid -- with respect to prepaid. Is it more a commentary on the macro environment and the saturation levels in the industry or is it more from the perspective of an origination pipeline? Obviously, the deal is accretive, financially, but strategically, what's the broader goals that you're hoping to solve with that.

And secondly, I guess, there's been a lot of headline last couple of days around the Google payment to carriers and the amount seems meaningful enough and it's pure margins for the most part. So if you could just help us understand how big revenue streams from application providers are and where that shows up in your P&L, that might be helpful? Thanks.

Hans Vestberg -- Chairman and Chief Executive Officer

